tps://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-plans-large-new-london-embassy-rejected-by-local-officials-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>国会可能禁止两家中国制造商生产新无人机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/dji-could-be-banned-launching-new-products-us-under-proposed-bill-2024-12-09/</link><description>根据美国众议院将于本周晚些时候投票的年度军事法案，中国大疆创新和 Autel Robotics 可能被禁止在美国市场销售新无人机。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 19:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/dji-could-be-banned-launching-new-products-us-under-proposed-bill-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>币安首席执行官滕表示，币安仍在选择全球总部地点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-still-choose-location-global-headquarters-ceo-teng-says-2024-12-09/</link><description>加密货币交易所币安网首席执行官周一对路透表示，该公司尚未决定其全球总部的设立地点，此前该公司曾表示即将做出决定，但该高管指出了该公司为改善公司治理而采取的举措。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-still-choose-location-global-headquarters-ceo-teng-says-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>法国欧安诺将与中国XTC成立两家合资企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/frances-orano-set-up-two-jvs-with-chinas-xtc-2024-12-09/</link><description>法国核电集团欧安诺周一宣布与中国XTC新能源材料集团成立两家合资企业，在法国敦刻尔克生产电动汽车电池组件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:53:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/frances-orano-set-up-two-jvs-with-chinas-xtc-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪在欧洲扩张中将重点关注插电式混合动力汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-focus-plug-in-hybrid-cars-european-expansion-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪在欧洲的特别顾问周一表示，由于全电动汽车需求疲软，混合动力技术将成为该公司在欧洲扩张的关键。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:54:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-focus-plug-in-hybrid-cars-european-expansion-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>在欧盟的中国企业表示，在全球紧张局势中，商业环境更加严峻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/business-conditions-tougher-chinese-firms-eu-say-amid-global-tensions-2024-12-09/</link><description>周一公布的一项调查显示，在欧盟的中国企业表示，商业环境连续第五年恶化，地缘政治紧张局势加剧和反华情绪阻碍了运营。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/business-conditions-tougher-chinese-firms-eu-say-amid-global-tensions-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>字节跳动、TikTok 寻求暂时停止美国禁令，等待最高法院审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/bytedance-tiktok-seek-temporary-halt-us-crackdown-law-pending-supreme-court-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国字节跳动及其短视频应用 TikTok 周一请求上诉法院暂时阻止一项法律，该法律要求母公司字节跳动在 1 月 19 日之前剥离 TikTok，否则将面临禁令，等待美国最高法院的审查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/bytedance-tiktok-seek-temporary-halt-us-crackdown-law-pending-supreme-court-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着需求不断增长，中国小米将于明年夏天推出新款 SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xiaomi-announces-new-suv-launch-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国电子产品制造商小米周一表示，预计将在明年 6 月或 7 月推出首款 SUV YU7，进一步进军中国竞争激烈的汽车市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xiaomi-announces-new-suv-launch-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>LGIM表示对中国不太乐观；英国后备母猪报价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-lgim-urgent-2024-12-09/</link><description>Legal &amp;amp; General Investment Management 首席投资官索尼娅·劳德 (Sonja Laud) 周一表示，中国仍面临非常困难的经济形势，目前还很难对世界第二大经济体持乐观态度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:19:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-lgim-urgent-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国针对英伟达展开反垄断调查，加剧美国芯片紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-investigates-nvidia-over-suspected-violation-antimonopoly-law-2024-12-09/</link><description>此次调查是在美国上周对中国半导体行业发起三年来的第三次打压之后进行的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 11:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-investigates-nvidia-over-suspected-violation-antimonopoly-law-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>美洲 美联储降息，中国改变货币立场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-09/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 11:10:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国货币宽松立场推动矿业股和能源股提振富时 100 指数</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/miners-propel-uks-ftse-100-higher-gdp-data-tap-2024-12-09/</link><description>英国富时 100 指数周一在能源和矿业股的推动下攀升，投资者关注本周的国内 GDP 数据来衡量英国央行的政策前景。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 10:27:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/miners-propel-uks-ftse-100-higher-gdp-data-tap-2024-12-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>